<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Successfuly Sign in</title>
    <style>
      * {
        color: #000;
      }

      .card {
        width: 500px;
        margin: 50px auto;
      }

      .dark {
        font-weight: 900;
        margin-right: 8px;
      }

      .logo_image {
        object-fit: contain;
        width: 200px;
      }

      p {
        line-height: 1.3;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      }

      a {
        color: #2827cc;
      }

      .logo {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="logo">
        <img
          src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/react-spring-boot-user-profile.appspot.com/o/images%2FAppointy.png?alt=media&token=b633f79a-868c-447a-b1ed-357e6ec0b863"
          alt="logo"
          class="logo_image"
        />
      </div>

      <p>We're verifying a recent sign-in for <%= templateData.email %> :</p>
      <p><span class="dark">Timestamp: </span> <%= templateData.timestamp %></p>
      <p><span class="dark">IP Address:</span><%= templateData.ip %></p>
      <p><span class="dark"> User agent: </span> <%= templateData.device %></p>
      <p>
        You're receiving this message because of a successful sign-in from a
        device that we didnâ€™t recognize. If you believe that this sign-in is
        suspicious, <a href="#"> please reset your password immediately.</a> If
        you're aware of this sign-in, please disregard this notice. This can
        happen when you use your browser's incognito or private browsing mode or
        clear your cookies.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 20px">
        Thanks , <br />
        Appointy Team
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
